reviewText:
I played with the Gentleman of the Row mod, some things may not be in the vanilla game. And for the love of god, use a gamepad.

It may not be the best port out there, it may not be the over the top silly memefest, but damn, this one is by far the best on the series. Packs together a very good plot, a crapton of things to do, and the best city ever made in an open world game. If you are into shooting things, exploding things, terrible controls and gangsta things, this one is right for you.

Pros:
Awesome storyline;
Actually good side activities;
A city worth exploring;
Great character customization;
Drive-by with katanas;
Really good characters;
Both funny and serious moments are well writen.

Cons:
Terrible, TERRIBLE PC port;
The Brotherhood;
Respect system kinda sucks;

Overall rating: 10/10, ballin' gangsta stuff rite here.
